In article <33fojv$3ae@sky.itr.ch>,
Heinzmann Peter <pheinzma@sky.itr.ch> wrote:
>We are currently updating our information about quantum cryptography.
>We know of several papers by C.H.Bennet, G.Brassard, et al up to
>1992. Can anybody point us to more recent work?

My book, Applied Cryptography, has an extensive list of references in
this field.  However, what you really want is:

	G. Brassard, "Cryptography column--Quantum Cryptography: A
	Bibliography," SIGACT NEWS, v 24, n 3, 1993, pp. 16-20.

It's an annotated bibliography of all the papers in the field.

Bruce
